      Step 1: Create the Kubernetes YAML File
      We need to tell Kubernetes to pull your image from Docker Hub and run it.
          1.Open VS Code.
          2.Create a new folder inside your project called k8s (this keeps things organized).
          3.Inside the k8s folder, create a file named v1-deploy.yaml.
